dc_title_s: Roads and ROW Juneau County, WI 2023
dc_description_s: This data represents roads and Right Of Ways (ROW) for Juneau County, Wisconsin in 2023 and includes the layers 'JUNEAU_ROADS_2023' and 'JUNEAU_ROW_2023'. [Roads: Roads data contain the centerlines of all the roads in the county. They are coded by class being: 5 - Interstates, 4 - US Highways, 3 - State Highways, 2 - County Trunk Roads, 1 - Town/Local Roads and 0 - Private Roads, Trails or Alleys. They also have an address range assigned to them with a right and left to and from range, the centerlines broken down into segments with what community (zipcode) they are in, and also what emergency zone (ESN) they fall in.]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison.
